data.description: This is an unparalleled opportunity to own a piece of luxury in the prestigious Quail Creek Estates.  This breathtaking 4,074 sq foot home is located on one of Quail Creeks most coveted lanes.  It features 4BR/3.5 BA offering both lake and golf views.   This is the first time this estate home has hit the market.  The original owners masterfully built this home with a versatile floor plan with no details overlooked.  The home has tons of natural lighting, while offering privacy to enjoy the beautiful sunsets that Naples has to offer.  The primary suite is a true oasis highlighted by luxurious his/her closets, spa-like primary bath with jetted tub and dual sinks.  The primary has an extra room (considered the 4th bedroom) that could be used as an exercise room or sitting room.  The chef's kitchen is a culinary delight with great counter space, and 2 built-in kitchen pantries.  Adjacent to the kitchen is an oversized family room with wet bar and fireplace creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and entertaining.  Step outside to discover a true paradise.  Oversized pool with screened-in sitting/dining area on lanai.  3 car garage and house generator.
